Catalyst-Plugin-ClamAV

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    CLAMAV_SOCKET_NAME=/var/run/clamd.sock make test
    make install

Set env your clamd's socket information.
  CLAMAV_SOCKET_NAME
  CLAMAV_SOCKET_HOST
  CLAMAV_SOCKET_POST

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the perldoc command.

    perldoc Catalyst::Plugin::ClamAV

You can also look for information at:

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Catalyst-Plugin-ClamAV

    CPAN Request Tracker:
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Catalyst-Plugin-ClamAV

    AnnoCPAN, annotated CPAN documentation:
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Catalyst-Plugin-ClamAV

    CPAN Ratings:
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Catalyst-Plugin-ClamAV

